high_descs: Walk over to the tub, then turn left and walk up to the wall.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn right and take a step forward, after that turn around.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
Take a step forward, then turn left and walk forward, turn right to face the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap that is on the edge of the tub.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn around to face the tub.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap into the tub.

high_descs: Move to face the towel right that's to the right of the toilet and look down.
Pick up the pink bar of soap that's on the right edge of the back of the toilet.
Turn right to the face the tub on the right.
Place the bar of soap in the tub and to the right of the blue rag on the left.
Move to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap on the edge of the tub.
Move to the front of the tub facing the first pink bar of soap in the tub.
Place the second pink bar of soap in the tub to the left of the first bar of soap and in front of the blue rag on the left.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of pink soap inside of the tub.

high_descs: walk to the left and stop in front of the wall between the toilet and bath tub
pick up the pink bar of soap from the top of the toilet tank
turn to the right and face the bath tub
put the pink bar of soap in the bath tub basin between the two purple flowers
continue to face the bath tub
pick up the pink bar of soap on the bath tub front edge
continue to face the bath tub
place the bar of soap to the left of the other bar of soap in the bath tub basin
anns.task_desc: put two bars of soap in the bath tub
